<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-63144dff-facb-4a05-8d07-84ab7a60478e">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-6dc81018-d6f3-48ec-b020-815cf1477153">Thank you for contacting the Claims Team.</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-3a5c80a4-ccd7-472a-8df1-318da0f3c1c0">We have received your email and one of our claims handlers will review it as soon as possible. If your message relates to a new claim, we will acknowledge it and let you know the next steps within 1–2 working days.</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-12f97cae-f816-492d-8e80-fb4187330311">For urgent matters, please contact us on <em class="ql-bg-red" style="background-color: red;">############</em>, Monday to Friday, 9 to 5.</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-3b0cd2ea-e1cf-4ae4-94f9-6499590f3a2d">If you have included any documents or claim forms, these will be actioned accordingly and will be added to your file.</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-c4a8984a-bbf4-44f4-a5b2-b5917c6366eb">Thank you for your patience – we’ll be in touch shortly.</div><p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">&nbsp;</p><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-471bc000-811c-440c-9340-9c057939a820">Kind regards</div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>